    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone looking for a functional daily driver. The engine runs consistently and the car handles well on the road, though it is due for a standard tune-up soon. The exterior has some visible scuffs and minor dings from regular use, and the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery, but all essential electronics and climate controls are fully operational. It is a solid, dependable vehicle that has been regularly serviced, even if it lacks the polish of a newer model.",
