    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, preserved in showroom condition and maintained to an uncompromising standard. This specimen represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire an automobile of truly immaculate character. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a legacy of meticulous stewardship. Its mechanical integrity is absolute, ensuring an automotive experience that remains indistinguishable from its original debut.",
      "price": 48500.0,
