      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, a masterclass in longitudinal front-midship engineering. This example retains its original 13B-REW twin-rotor powerplant, featuring a flawlessly functioning sequential twin-turbocharger system that delivers linear boost across the rev range. The chassis maintains a perfect 50/50 weight distribution, supported by factory double-wishbone suspension with no bushing degradation. The 5-speed manual transmission exhibits crisp synchromesh engagement, feeding power through a Torsen limited-slip differential. Recent compression testing confirms all rotor faces are well within factory specifications. The exterior retains its factory-applied finish with zero evidence of oxidation or clear coat failure, while the interior remains free of bolster wear or dash warping. This is a collector-grade specimen with a cooling system that has been fastidiously maintained to prevent heat soak, ensuring the thermal integrity of the apex seals.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
